summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting deeds for street/alley purposes in Block 10, Plat of Ravenna Springs Park, Southeast Quarter of Section 19, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M., Block 50, Sea View Park, and Block 2, White and Manning's Addition to West Seattle, laying off Northeast 60th Street, Stone Avenue North, the alley in Block 50, Sea View Park, Fauntleroy Way Southwest, Southwest Avalon Way, and Southwest Yancy Street (RW 8812, RW 8952, RW 8954 and RW 8959).
